recordedBy: Edith L. Taylor|Carlos S. Rosário|J.B.F. da Silva
locality: Municipio Grajau; Mondelandia (42km. N from BR226 on road that leaves highway E of Grajau). terra devoluta of Sr. Pesoa (sp?), 4 km. W of Mondelandia on path that runs to Rio Grajau and ultimately to Balaio. 1000 hectares of transition forest on ridge above capoiera sout of the path. Transition forest is relatively undisturbed short wit a few large emergents. Level, relatively undisturbed (some charcoal in soil), understory open, some areas of tree fall with many vines. The only mature forest in the entire region; the rest has been clearcut. Pariana dominates understory; Rutaceae and Rubiaceaem subcanopy; Cenostigma, Duguetia, Annoa, Cassia, Dipteryx, Guabiraba (Myrtaceae) canopy.
